{"type":null,"faqId":32802,"title":"为什么摄像头用几个月以后在画面中发现有黑点和脏污？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、首先将摄像头后方保护镜片擦拭干净，确保镜片没有弄脏。同时确认保护镜片是否已经被其它尖锐物品刮伤。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、如果还是存在脏污情况则是您使用过程中出现过摔落等情况导致摄像头内部掉落碎屑从而表现出黑点和脏污的情况。由于模组属于精密设备无法拆开，此时将手机屏幕正对您，左手静止，右手握住手机在左手上拍打等震动的方式将碎屑拍出摄像头成像区域则可使拍照时不受影响。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3、如果还存在，则建议联系最近的维修点去进行处理。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7504","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748409000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":35,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"摄像头,黑点,脏污","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}